Package: icescrapr
Type: Package
Title: A package for scraping and summarizing PbP Data from NHL.com
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author@R: person("Eric", "Fastner", email = "eric.fastner@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Maintainer: Eric Fastner <eric.fastner@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of functions that will help the user srape
    play-by-play data from NHL.com as well as a collection of functions
    for summarizing, analyzing, and visualizing the results. Special thanks to
    Evolving Hockey (https://evolving-hockey.com/) for the scraping functions
